title: Picture, ca. 1865
description: White silk ribbon brocaded with portraits of Eugenie and Napoleon III, enclosed in much floral ornament in shades of green and lavendar; ribbon edge picoted in lavendar. At lower right, woven initials and date: LF Ce 1865.

Technique: jacquard woven. Gift of Anonymous Donor. a-t-776.
